This is a Chinese buffet I would actually recommend for a friend. They have scrumptious food. And variety of dishes, they got everything. They even try to make American food like mashed potatoes with gravy sausages and mac and cheese it's a great place for kids as well. It's clean the silverware is clean you serve your own drinks they are constantly refilling the the food so the food is always hot you don't have to worry about E.coli and all that stuff. If y'all have noticed a lot of buffets are closing down because of food poisoning. Apparently this establishment has been around for longtime said Business. So they don't have a website Flyers they only have a phone number and an address but they stay and out when you're driving so you can't miss it. you can even take some food home you can order it to go if you would like. It's only $11 and done change. Theygive you a nice styrofoam container with a bowl for your rice on the side. One thing I really dislike about this place is the parking.
